name: Organization Attributes
attributes:
- Type: Corporation, Government, Non-profit, Educational, Religious, Criminal, Military
- Size: 1 to 1,000,000 members/employees
- Founding Year: 1700 to 2023
- Influence: 1 to 10 scale
- Wealth: 1 to 10 scale
- Corruption: 1 to 10 scale
- Ideology: Textual description of guiding principles
- Leadership Structure: Autocratic, Democratic, Oligarchic, Meritocratic, Anarchic, Bureaucratic
- Publicly Traded: Yes or No
- Description: General description and notable information
